## Summary
This documentation page explains Amplitude's Lifecycle Chart feature, which categorizes active users into new, current, and returning segments while also tracking dormant users, allowing product teams to visualize user base growth over time and identify engagement patterns through different chart views (Growth, Dormant, and Pulse).

